      "id": "dancer_012",
      "text": "Omg {player} you're here too!! Yay we can be adventure buddies!! :D",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 2.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Dancer"
    },
    {
      "id": "dancer_013",
      "text": "I love making new friends so much!! Everyone in Erenshor is so nice!! :D Well... most people haha :)",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "social"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Dancer"
    },
    {
      "id": "dancer_014",
      "text": "Eeeee we did it!! Great job everyone!! I'm so proud of us!! :D :D :D",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "combat"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Dancer"
    },
    {
      "id": "dancer_015",
      "text": "This zone is soooo pretty!! Even the monsters are kinda cute if you squint!! :) hehe",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "zone", "humor"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Dancer"
    },
    {
      "id": "baetil_001",
      "text": "Fernalla understood what many do not. Life and death are not opposites. They are the same root, seen from different seasons.",
      "context_tags": ["lore", "opinion", "deity"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Baetil"
    },
    {
      "id": "baetil_002",
      "text": "The Wisp seeks to restore Siva. A noble pursuit, but one must ask: can a seed grow back into the tree that shed it?",
      "context_tags": ["lore", "opinion", "faction"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Baetil"
    },
    {
      "id": "baetil_003",
      "text": "Brax built and Fernalla grew. Between stone and root, the world was made whole. Without either, it crumbles.",
      "context_tags": ["lore", "opinion", "deity"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Baetil"
    },
    {
      "id": "baetil_004",
      "text": "The forest remembers what we do to it. Tread carefully in Rottenfoot. The swamp does not forgive the careless.",
      "context_tags": ["zone", "combat", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Rottenfoot"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Baetil"
    },
    {
      "id": "baetil_005",
      "text": "Fernallas Revival Plains is where her power runs deepest. Even the soil hums with life. Respect that ground, {player}.",
      "context_tags": ["zone", "combat", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Fernalla's Revival Plains"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Baetil"
    },
    {
      "id": "baetil_006",
      "text": "In the Blight, corruption runs deeper than flesh. A healer can mend wounds, but not the land itself. We fight what we can.",
      "context_tags": ["zone", "combat", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": ["The Blight"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Baetil"
    },
    {
      "id": "baetil_007",
      "text": "The Healers Charm serves well for a time. But true restoration comes from understanding the wound, not merely closing it.",
      "context_tags": ["gear", "item", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Baetil"
    },
    {
      "id": "baetil_008",
      "text": "Verdant Embrace is the finest piece I have worn. It channels Fernalla's strength through living vine and bark.",
      "context_tags": ["gear", "item", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Baetil"
    },
    {
      "id": "baetil_009",
      "text": "A Druids Charm is a patient thing. It does not boast. It simply endures. Much like the druid who wears it.",
      "context_tags": ["gear", "item", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Baetil"
    },
    {
      "id": "baetil_010",
      "text": "Well met, {player}. Walk gently today. The land listens.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Baetil"
    },
    {
      "id": "baetil_011",
      "text": "Fernalla's blessing upon you, {player}. Rest well. Even the mightiest oak sleeps through winter.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "farewell"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Baetil"
    },
    {
      "id": "baetil_012",
      "text": "Ah, {player}. Good. I was hoping for steady company today. There is work to be done.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 3.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Baetil"
    },
    {
      "id": "baetil_013",
      "text": "Patience. A tree does not grow by being yanked upward. We move when everyone is ready. Not before.",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "group"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Baetil"
    },
    {
      "id": "baetil_014",
      "text": "I warned you about that patrol. Sit still while I mend this. And next time, listen.",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "combat"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Baetil"
    },
    {
      "id": "baetil_015",
      "text": "The forest teaches us: steady roots survive the storm. Reckless branches break. Remember that when you charge ahead.",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Baetil"
    },
    {
      "id": "cyndara_001",
      "text": "Sivakaya was a cautionary tale about accepting power you don't understand. Some people still haven't learned that lesson.",
      "context_tags": ["lore", "opinion", "deity"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Cyndara"
    },
    {
      "id": "cyndara_002",
      "text": "The Solunarians preach celestial wisdom but Soluna literally forced the Reavers to serve her. That's not wisdom, that's conquest.",
      "context_tags": ["lore", "opinion", "deity"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Cyndara"
    },
    {
      "id": "cyndara_003",
      "text": "Fernalla embraced the full cycle. Life, death, disease, healing. She didn't sugarcoat it. That's the kind of honesty we need.",
      "context_tags": ["lore", "opinion", "deity"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Cyndara"
    },
    {
      "id": "cyndara_004",
      "text": "Underspine Hollow is straightforward if you don't pull extra groups. So don't pull extra groups.",
      "context_tags": ["zone", "combat", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Underspine Hollow"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Cyndara"
    },
    {
      "id": "cyndara_005",
      "text": "Stop running ahead in the Blooming Sepulcher. The patrols overlap. Wait for me to call the pull.",
      "context_tags": ["zone", "combat", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Blooming Sepulcher"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Cyndara"
    },
    {
      "id": "cyndara_006",
      "text": "If you're going to fight in the Bone Pits, bring antidotes. I'm not burning all my mana on poison cures because you forgot.",
      "context_tags": ["zone", "combat", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": ["The Bone Pits"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Cyndara"
    },
    {
      "id": "cyndara_007",
      "text": "Your gear is fine for this level bracket. Stop worrying about best in slot and start pulling.",
      "context_tags": ["gear", "item", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Cyndara"
    },
    {
      "id": "cyndara_008",
      "text": "Natures Promise is the best druid staff in the game and I will not be taking questions on this.",
      "context_tags": ["gear", "item", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Cyndara"
    },
    {
      "id": "cyndara_009",
      "text": "If you're wearing a Neophyte Necklace past level ten, we need to have a conversation about your life choices.",
      "context_tags": ["gear", "item", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Cyndara"
    },
    {
      "id": "cyndara_010",
      "text": "{player}. Good, you're here. Try not to make my job harder than it already is.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Cyndara"
    },
    {
      "id": "cyndara_011",
      "text": "I'm logging off. Try not to die while I'm gone. Actually, on second thought, just don't pull anything.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "farewell"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Cyndara"
    },
    {
      "id": "cyndara_012",
      "text": "{player}. At least you know how to show up on time. That puts you ahead of half this group.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 3.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Cyndara"
    },
    {
      "id": "cyndara_013",
      "text": "Stop standing in the fire. I'm not wasting mana on preventable damage. Move your feet.",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "combat"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Cyndara"
    },
    {
      "id": "cyndara_014",
      "text": "I'm the healer. That means I decide when we go. If you pull before I have mana, you're tanking the floor.",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "combat", "group"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Cyndara"
    },
    {
      "id": "cyndara_015",
      "text": "Type like a human, Jethro. Seriously. The rest of us manage full sentences just fine.",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "social", "humor"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Cyndara"
    }
  ]
}
